'''季风宫'''（{{Lang-en|'''Monsoon Palace'''}}）位于印度[[拉贾斯坦邦|拉贾斯坦邦]][[乌代布尔|乌代布尔]]郊外的[[阿拉瓦利岭|阿拉瓦利岭]]山顶，俯瞰法塔赫湖。季风宫由当地土王建于1884年，可以欣赏该市的湖泊、宫殿和周围乡野的景色，并可欣赏日出和日落美景<ref name=sajjan>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rajasthantourism.gov.in/Destinations/Udaipur/Sajjangarh.aspx|title=Sajjangarh|accessdate=2009-11-13|publisher=Rajasthan Tourism|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091029111035/http://www.rajasthantourism.gov.in/Destinations/Udaipur/Sajjangarh.aspx|archivedate=2009-10-29}}</ref><ref name=udai>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rajasthantourism.gov.in/Destinations/Udaipur.aspx|title=Udaipur|accessdate=2009-11-13|publisher=Rajasthan Tourism|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091114005850/http://www.rajasthantourism.gov.in/Destinations/Udaipur.aspx|archivedate=2009-11-14}}</ref><ref name=monsoon>{{Cite web|url=http://www.asiarooms.com/travel-guide/india/udaipur/sightseeing-in-udaipur/monsoon-palace-(sajjan-garh).html|title=Monsoon Palace (Sajjan Garh)|accessdate=2009-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090515012816/http://www.asiarooms.com/travel-guide/india/udaipur/sightseeing-in-udaipur/monsoon-palace-(sajjan-garh).html|archive-date=2009-05-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name= Bindloss>{{Cite book|last=Bindloss|first=Joe|author2=Sarina Singh|title=India|work=Sajjan Garh|page=221|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=T7ZHUhSEleYC&pg=PA221&dq=Monsoon+Palace#v=onepage&q=Monsoon%20Palace&f=false|publisher=Lonely Planet|year=2007|isbn=9781741043082|access-date=2016-02-01|archive-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705104617/http://books.google.com/books?id=T7ZHUhSEleYC&pg=PA221&dq=Monsoon+Palace#v=onepage&q=Monsoon%20Palace&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Stott>{{Cite book|last=Stott|first=David|title=Footprint Rajasthan|work=Monsoon Palace|page=194|accessdate=2009-11-14|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=igdKYE-fNcAC&pg=PA194&dq=Monsoon+Palace&lr=#v=onepage&q=Monsoon%20Palace&f=false|publisher=Footprint Travel Guides|year=2007|isbn=9781906098070|archive-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705104031/http://books.google.com/books?id=igdKYE-fNcAC&pg=PA194&dq=Monsoon+Palace&lr=#v=onepage&q=Monsoon%20Palace&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Mewar>{{Cite web|url=http://www.eternalmewar.in/User/Research/WikiDescription.aspx?Id=Sajjangarh|title=Sajjangarh|accessdate=2009-11-14|publisher=Eteranl Mewar|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721155546/http://www.eternalmewar.in/User/Research/WikiDescription.aspx?Id=Sajjangarh|archivedate=2011-07-21}}</ref><ref name =fodders>{{Cite web|url=http://www.fodors.com/world/asia/india/rajasthan-and-gujarat/review-110589.html|title=Sajjan Garh|accessdate=2009-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091006075343/http://www.fodors.com/world/asia/india/rajasthan-and-gujarat/review-110589.html|archive-date=2009-10-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。季风宫原来属于土王，现在由拉贾斯坦邦林业局管理，对公众开放。

季风宫曾出现在1983年[[詹姆斯·邦德|詹姆斯·邦德]]电影《[[八爪女|八爪女]]》中。

